Description: # botele
        ### Python Telegram Bot Factory
        
        ## Installation
        ```bash
        $ pip install botele
        ```
        ## Basic Usage
        ```bash
        $ mkdir mybot
        $ cd mybot
        $ botele setup .
        $ echo "<BOT TOKEN>" > mybot.token
        $ vim mybot.py # Write your bot file
        ...
        $ botele make # Checks for bot consistency
        $ botele install
        $ botele list
        Available bots:
                 1. mybot
        $ botele run mybot # Here we go!
        > Started Polling, going idle.
        ```
        
